title: Stanislav Zakharchenko
text:
Stanislav Igorevich Zakharchenko (; born 1 January 1994) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Second%20Division">Russian Second Division</a> for <a href="FC%20Taganrog">FC Taganrog</a> on 18 September 2011 in a game against <a href="FC%20Rotor%20Volgograd">FC Rotor Volgograd</a>.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20Mordovia%20Saransk">FC Mordovia Saransk</a> on 31 July 2016 in a game against <a href="FC%20SKA-Khabarovsk">FC SKA-Khabarovsk</a>.
